Class Account

java.lang.Object
models.Account
Direct Known Subclasses:
Patient, Staff
public abstract class Account extends Object
Represents an abstract Account in the system. This class is the base class for different types of accounts (e.g., Administrator, Staff). It provides common attributes and methods for managing account details such as user ID, name, password, and role.
